								<div class="title" id="post-title-2245790">
																		AUTOR BEITRAG
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/agent-macleod" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1922529); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1922529&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610250810" alt="Agent MacLeod" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1922529)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/agent-macleod" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1922529); return false;" >Agent MacLeod</a></span> <span class="odate time_1425631820 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">06 Mar 2015 08:50</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2245790">
									

<p>Huge thanks to Randomini, TwistedGears, and Decibelle for looking in chat, thanks to <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">Flameshirt</span> SoundChaser for telling me who would've succeeded Winston Churchill had Winston Churchill been blown up, and to anyone else who helped.</p>
<p>The lowercase on the title is intentional, don't touch it.</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Spoilers</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>The Australian contact? He's either cut a deal with <a href="/scp-1917">SCP-1917</a>, or he's cutting her into pieces in order to make this thing. Either interpretation is valid. Entity KOLOSS may or may not be a wee little thing from the Old Testament called the Behemoth. As far as what it's reimagining, it's the one or two living tank skips in Series I, and <a href="/scp-044">SCP-044</a>. More reimagining the idea of Foundationverse wunderwaffe than anything.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>Any questions, ask!</p>

